#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Simplified Hibernate with Quarkus Data Hibernate"
msgstr "使用 Quarkus Data Hibernate 简化 Hibernate"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"This extension requests early feedback to mature the idea\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">experimental</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"此扩展程序希望征集早期反馈以完善该构想\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">实验性</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Data Hibernate is the perfect solution if you want to get started using Hibernate in Quarkus."
msgstr "如果您想在 Quarkus 中开始使用 Hibernate，Quarkus Data Hibernate 就是最佳解决方案。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This extension is currently experimental, so its API may change, in particular names of\n"
"classes or packages may change, even the module name. We are in the process of making it a public preview in order\n"
"to obtain public feedback, so please report feedback either on link:https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Panache.2ENext/with/562916276[Zulip]\n"
"or via link:https://github.com/orgs/quarkusio/projects/50/views/1[GitHub issues]."
msgstr "该扩展目前处于实验阶段，因此其 API 可能会发生变化，尤其是类或包的名称可能会变更，甚至模块名称也可能变更。我们正在将其转为公开预览版，以便收集公众反馈，因此请在 link:https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Panache.2ENext/with/562916276[Zulip] 上或通过 link:https://github.com/orgs/quarkusio/projects/50/views/1[GitHub 问题] 提交反馈。"

#. type: Title =
