msgstr "让我们采取循序渐进的方式来学习如何使用 Quarkus Data Hibernate，并从一个简单的实体开始。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide is not going to go into the specifics of using either\n"
"xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate], or its underlying\n"
"link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}[Jakarta Persistence specification],\n"
"because both already have great documentation that you can and should use for more in-depth knowledge."
msgstr "本指南不会深入探讨 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate] 或其底层 link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}[Jakarta Persistence 规范] 的具体用法，因为这两者都已提供了非常详尽的文档，您可以且应当参考这些文档以获取更深入的知识。"

