msgid "REST integration"
msgstr "REST 集成"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When your application uses both `quarkus-data-hibernate` and `quarkus-rest-jackson`, Quarkus automatically\n"
"adds REST support for common Jakarta Data parameter types. This lets you declare Jakarta Data types directly as\n"
"REST endpoint parameters, and they will be populated from HTTP query parameters without any manual parsing."
msgstr "当您的应用程序同时使用 `quarkus-data-hibernate` 和 `quarkus-rest-jackson` 时，Quarkus 会自动为常见的 Jakarta Data 参数类型添加 REST 支持。这使您可以直接将 Jakarta Data 类型声明为 REST 端点参数，系统会自动从 HTTP 查询参数中获取数据，无需任何手动解析。"

