#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Cursor-based pagination (`PageRequest.Mode.CURSOR_NEXT` / `CURSOR_PREVIOUS`) is not currently supported\n"
"by this REST integration. Only offset-based pagination is available via query parameters."
msgstr "此 REST 集成目前不支持基于光标的分页（ `PageRequest.Mode.CURSOR_NEXT` / `CURSOR_PREVIOUS` ）。仅支持通过查询参数实现基于偏移量的分页。"

#. type: Title ==
