#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Page serialization"
msgstr "页面序列化"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When a REST endpoint returns a `jakarta.data.page.Page`, it is serialized as a JSON object with pagination\n"
"metadata, rather than as a plain array:"
msgstr "当 REST 端点返回一个 `jakarta.data.page.Page` 对象时，它会被序列化为一个包含分页元数据的 JSON 对象，而不是一个普通的数组："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `totalElements` and `totalPages` fields are only included when the `PageRequest` was created with\n"
"`requestTotal=true`."
msgstr "只有当 `PageRequest` 的创建时 `requestTotal=true` 时，才会包含 `totalElements` 和 `totalPages` 字段。"

