#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`PageRequest` is populated from `page`, `size`, and `requestTotal` query parameters.\n"
"`Order` is populated from repeating `sort` query parameters."
msgstr "`PageRequest` 的值来自 `page` 、 `size` 和 `requestTotal` 查询参数。 `Order` 的值来自 repeating `sort` 查询参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A client can then call:"
msgstr "然后，客户端可以调用："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This produces a `PageRequest.ofPage(1, 20, true)` and `Order.by(Sort.asc(\"name\"), Sort.desc(\"birth\"))`."
msgstr "这会生成一个 `PageRequest.ofPage(1, 20, true)` 和 `Order.by(Sort.asc(\"name\"), Sort.desc(\"birth\"))` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "HQL, JD-QL, Jakarta-QL, Panache-QL"
msgstr "HQL、JD-QL、Jakarta-QL、Panache-QL"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are different query languages used in this API:"
msgstr "该 API 中使用了多种查询语言："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:https://docs.hibernate.org/orm/{hibernate-orm-version-major-minor}/querylanguage/html_single/[Hibernate Query Language] (HQL),\n"
"which is the query language used by Hibernate, supported by the `@HQL` annotation."
msgstr "link:https://docs.hibernate.org/orm/{hibernate-orm-version-major-minor}/querylanguage/html_single/[Hibernate 查询语言] （HQL）是 Hibernate 使用的查询语言，由 `@HQL` 注解提供支持。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}#a4665[Jakarta Persistence Query Language] (JP-QL), which is a subset of the Hibernate\n"
"Query Language. It is currently being moved to its own spec called\n"
"link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/query/1.0/jakarta-query-1.0-m1[Jakarta Query]."
msgstr "link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}#a4665[雅加达持久化查询语言] （JP-QL）是 Hibernate 查询语言的一个子集。目前，它正在迁移到一个名为 link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/query/1.0/jakarta-query-1.0-m1[“雅加达查询] ”（ link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/query/1.0/jakarta-query-1.0-m1[Jakarta Query] ）的独立规范中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:{jakarta-data-spec-url}#_jakarta_data_query_language[Jakarta Data Query Language] (JD-QL), which is a subset of the\n"
"Jakarta Persistence Query Language, supported by the `@Query` annotation."
msgstr "link:{jakarta-data-spec-url}#_jakarta_data_query_language[雅加达数据查询语言] （JD-QL）是雅加达持久化查询语言的一个子集，由 `@Query` 注解提供支持。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Panache Query Language, which is a superset of the Hibernate Query Language adding very few shortcuts, which\n"
"is supported in all the `PanacheRepository` queries."
msgstr "Panache 查询语言是 Hibernate 查询语言的超集，仅添加了极少的快捷方式，所有 `PanacheRepository` 查询均支持该语言。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Panache Query Language"
msgstr "Panache 查询语言"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Normally, most HQL queries are of this form: `from EntityName [where ...] [order by ...]`, with optional elements\n"
"at the end."
msgstr "通常，大多数 HQL 查询都采用以下形式： `from EntityName [where …​] [order by …​]` ，末尾可选一些元素。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If your select query does not start with `from`, `select` or `with`, we support the following additional forms:"
msgstr "如果您的 SELECT 查询不以 `FROM` 、 `SELECT` 或 `WITH` 开头，我们支持以下其他形式："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`order by ...` which will expand to `from EntityName order by ...`"
msgstr "`order by …​` ，这将展开为 `from EntityName order by …​`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`<singleAttribute>` (and single parameter) which will expand to `from EntityName where <singleAttribute> = ?`"
msgstr "`<singleAttribute>` （以及单个参数），该表达式将展开为 `来自 EntityName，其中 <singleAttribute> = ?`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`where <query>` will expand to `from EntityName where <query>`"
msgstr "`其中 <query>` 将展开为 `from EntityName where <query>`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`<query>` will expand to `from EntityName where <query>`"
msgstr "`<query>` 将展开为 `from EntityName where <query>`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If your update query does not start with `update`, we support the following additional forms:"
msgstr "如果您的更新查询不以 `update` 开头，我们还支持以下其他形式："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`from EntityName ...` which will expand to `update EntityName ...`"
msgstr "`来自 EntityName …​` ，这将展开为 `更新 EntityName …​`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`set? <singleAttribute>` (and single parameter) which will expand to `update EntityName set <singleAttribute> = ?`"
msgstr "`set? <singleAttribute>` （以及单个参数），这将展开为 `update EntityName set <singleAttribute> = ?`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
