#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If your delete query does not start with `delete`, we support the following additional forms:"
msgstr "如果您的删除查询不以 `“delete”` 开头，我们还支持以下其他形式："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`from EntityName ...` which will expand to `delete from EntityName ...`"
msgstr "`from EntityName …​` 这将展开为 `delete from EntityName …​`"

