#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Security provides an initial support for securing Panache Repositories with security annotations."
msgstr "Quarkus Security 提供了通过安全注解保护 Panache 存储库的初步支持。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Example inner repository with method-level security annotations"
msgstr "包含方法级安全注解的示例内部存储库"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Example standalone repository with class-level security annotation"
msgstr "包含类级安全注解的独立仓库示例"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the example above, only methods directly declared on the `SecuredCatRepo` interface are secured.\n"
"Methods inherited from `PanacheRepository`, such as `findById`, `persist`, or `deleteAll`, are not secured because type-level annotations only affect the type they annotate."
