#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Currently, generic interface methods using type variables or wildcards cannot be secured reliably with standard security annotations.\n"
"Therefore, you must not attempt to secure such methods and instead use two alternatives described below."
msgstr "目前，使用类型变量或通配符的通用接口方法无法通过标准安全注解得到可靠的安全保障。因此，请勿尝试对这类方法进行安全加固，而应采用下文所述的两种替代方案。"

